<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
    <h2>Request to Redeem Reward</h2>

    <p>Dear Agency,</p>

    <p>We want to inform you that a user has sent a request to redeem a reward. Here are the details:</p>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Name:</strong> <%= donor.name %></li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= donor.email %></li>
        <li><strong>Username:</strong> <%= donor.username %></li>
        <li><strong>Contact:</strong> <%= donor.contact %></li>
    </ul>

    <p>The user has requested to redeem the following reward:</p>
    
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Name:</strong> <%= reward.name %></li>
        <li><strong>Points:</strong> <%= reward.points %></li>
    </ul>

    <p>This reward was earned by providing supplies for composting and contributing to saving food and the environment.</p>

    <p>Please review the request and take appropriate action.</p>

    <p>Thank you.</p>
</div>
